column1: Q32b. Can you tell me what impact, or what difference, you think the adviser made?
Base: Those whose advisor played a part
Helped improve my confidence / motivated me
Gave me useful information i.e. useful contact names and numbers
Helped me towards getting a job inc. updating my CV, interview techniques
Made me able to take stock of my skills and make plans for the future
Helped me with studying / returning to study
